modDescription:
This mod adds flower decor blocks to the game.

Guppycur had a request for some flowers in a vase. He could only find one free one but he did find a bunch of other flowers, so he made a pack of them.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Flower_Bunch_Blocks)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
